                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朝霞公司；变革型领导行为；民营企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ZhaoXia Company; Transformational Leadership Behaviors; Private Business</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以朝霞公司发展为主线，描述了朝霞公司总经理赵无忌采取一系列变革型领导行为，抢抓机遇，大胆变革，通过员工持股、外聘高管、绿色生产等管理措施，破解公司发展困境，推动公司稳步发展。旨在引发学员对民营企业变革型领导行为的思考和启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case focuses on the development of ZhaoXia Company, describes that Zhao Wuji, the general manager of ZhaoXia Company, adopts a series of transformational leadership behaviours, seizes the opportunity, boldly changes, and cracks the company&#39;s development dilemma and promotes the company&#39;s steady development through the management measures of employee shareholding, external executives, and green production. It aims to trigger participants&#39; thinking and inspiration on transformational leadership behaviours in private enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
